column5: Welcome aboard and you have caught some beauty fish in the past. Thanks for sharing the pics and will be watching for more.  Mike

Greetings everyone,  Not sure if it's the right place to post this but here it goes.....my name is Jacques..... I'm new to this site and I'm from the Outaouais region and enjoy fishing for all species of fish.  I like reading reports of outings of other fishermen, including pictures of fish of all size..... does'nt have to be a monster for me to appreciate it..... I try to go fishing when ever I can and truly enjoy being out on the water.  The species I target mostly are walley, pike and bass..... Had the opportunity to try musky hunting for the first time this year with Steve aka TroutnMuskyHunter and my friend Paul managed to land a 44" beast that put up a hell of a fight.  This site is fishermen dream with all of the information that it contains and so many reports being posted..... Congratulations  On a final note, would like to share some of the catches I was fortunate enough to catch...... here it goes...  ......  Leechman
Great stuff, welcome aboard!
